OL,3,CWelsh Government announces more
OL,4,Csupport for 'worst performing health
OL,5,Cboard'
OL,7,FThe Welsh Government has announced
OL,8,Ffurther help for Wales' largest health
OL,9,Fboard as its "performance issues
OL,10,Fremain" and continue to "pose risks to
OL,11,Fpatient safety and public confidence".
OL,13,FBetsi Cadwaladr University Health
OL,14,FBoard covers north Wales and it
OL,15,Fcontinues to struggle despite being
OL,16,Fplaced in special measures in February
OL,17,F2023.
