OL,3,CWelsh Government announces more
OL,4,Csupport for 'worst performing health
OL,5,Cboard'
OL,7,FWales' Cabinet Secretary for Health
OL,8,Fand Social Care, Jeremy Miles MS, said
OL,9,Fthe action was necessary to address
OL,10,F"significant and persistent
OL,11,Fchallenges" in delivering safe, timely
OL,12,Fand effective care.
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government said that people
OL,15,Fare experiencing unacceptably long
OL,16,Fwaiting times for both planned and
OL,17,Femergency care and leaders at the
OL,18,Fhealth board have asked for extra help
OL,19,Fto accelerate improvement.
