OL,5,Cboard'
OL,7,FA team of experts will be drafted in
OL,8,Fto support those already in charge at
OL,9,Fthe Health Board. Jeremy Miles has
OL,10,Fsaid they will not replace personnel
OL,11,Fbut offer support for six months and
OL,12,Fthen it will be reviewed.
OL,14,FThey will concentrate on reducing
OL,15,Fambulance handover delays and
OL,16,Fimproving flow, reducing waiting times
OL,17,Ffor planned treatment and diagnostic
OL,18,Ftests, improving waiting times for
OL,19,Fcancer diagnosis and treatment and
OL,20,Ffurther strengthening governance,
OL,21,Fassurance, and leadership capability.
