OL,7,FIn a public accountability meeting
OL,8,Fbetween Mr Miles and bosses at the
OL,9,FHealth Board on Thursday, November 20,
OL,10,Fthe Health Minister said that Betsi
OL,11,FCadwaladr was Wales' "worst performing
OL,12,Fhealth board and that's been a
OL,13,Fconsistent picture in cancer and
OL,14,Fplaned care and urgent and emergency
OL,15,Fcare."
