OL,5,Cboard'
OL,7,FHe said that the health board was
OL,8,Ffacing "significant challenges" in
OL,9,Fthose areas but commended the
OL,10,F"proactive approach" taken by the
OL,11,Fhealth board in requesting additional
OL,12,Fsupport to accelerate improvement.
OL,14,FPlaid Cymru's health spokesperson,
OL,15,FMabon ap Gwynfor, has raised concerns
OL,16,Fover Labour's handling of the board.
