OL,5,Cboard'
OL,7,F"This is a failure entirely of this
OL,8,FLabour Government's own making," he
OL,9,Fsaid. "They sacked the board and
OL,10,Fappointed their own people and
OL,11,Fappointed a new Chief Executive not
OL,12,Flong afterwards. Now they are saying
OL,13,Fthat they want to appoint more people.
OL,15,F"We have said numerous times that the
OL,16,Fescalation measures framework is not
OL,17,Ffit for purpose and clinicians, health
OL,18,Fmanagers and the public have lost
OL,19,Ffaith in it. Instead of listening to
OL,20,Fus this Labour Government went ahead
OL,21,Fand made it even more convoluted."
